Question 1
 The symbol for negation of proposition ‘p’ is

Response: ∼

Correct : ∼

Score: 1 out of 1 Yes

Question 2
 If p and q are two propositions, then the logical statement p Ù (p Ú q) º p and p Ú (p Ù q) º p follows which law of logic?

Response: Absorption law

Correct : Absorption law

Score: 1 out of 1 Yes

Question 3
